About Hidden Creek Golf Carts
Buying a new or preowned golf cart is a smart way to get what you want at a good value. We are proud to carry an unparalleled selection of
golf cart
in the Brooksville area. You'll find a pleasant range of prices and quality brands like
Club Car®
or Evolution EV, making it easier to find the golf cart that fits your personal budget requirements.
Our experienced sales staff is available to help you make an informed decision, and our friendly financing, service, and parts departments are prepared to make sure your experience is outstanding.
Contact Us
Call us at (813) 780-1000 or come by today and experience our superior service and selection! We look forward to serving youing. At Hidden Creek Golf Carts, we value the opportunity to create long term relationships with our customers.
​​​​​​​Contact Us
Hidden Creek Golf Carts is conveniently located near the areas of Webster, Ayers, Bayport, and Nobleton.
